                            'He observes you in silence, then pretends to yawn. “Brilliant. As far as I care, you can leave your pouch en bugger off. I help ma neighbors sell what they have in abundance, or divide things among our workers, builders, and travelers. If you want something, let’s get to it. Name’s {color=#f6d6bd}Akakios{/color}.”
                            '
                            '(akakios1 preset)':
                                pass
                    '“I’m looking for a trader.”' ( condition="at == 'distanced'" ):
                        $ narrator.add_history(kind='nvl', who=narrator.name, what='(distanced) - “I’m looking for a trader.”')
                        $ at_activate = 0
                        $ at = 0
                        $ howlersdell_akakios_friendship += 1
                        $ description_akakios01 = "He’s the treasurer of the village, responsible for distributing the supplies among the denizens, and for exchanging what’s left with outsiders."
                        menu:
                            '“You will ne find much of a marketplace here, but you’re at the right spot. Everyone brings here what they have in abundance, en I either sell it to travelers, or divide it among the workers, builders, artisans. These things here are ne {i}mine{/i},” he runs his eyes over the crates and barrels, “en I would ne call maself a {i}trader{/i}. I’m just {color=#f6d6bd}Akakios{/color}. But I can show you our wares, if you want.”
